msgid "5 Minutes"
msgstr "5 minuter"

msgid ""
"A sequential IO will bypass the cache once it passes this threshold. "
"(default:4.0M, max:3.9G)"
msgstr ""
"Sekventiell I/O kringgår cachen när den passerar det här tröskelvärdet "
"(standard: 4,0 M, max: 3,9 G)."

msgid ""
"Allow bcache go around the cache when there's read / write congestion. "
"(default:true)"
msgstr ""
"Tillåt bcache att kringgå cachen vid överbelastning av läsning eller "
"skrivning (standard: sant)."

msgid "Backing Devices"
msgstr "Bakomliggande enheter"

msgid "Bcache"
msgstr "Bcache"

msgid "Bcache Device"
msgstr "Bcache-enhet"

msgid "Cache Device"
msgstr "Cache-enhet"

msgid "Cache Devices"
msgstr "Cache-enheter"

msgid "Cache Mode"
msgstr "Cacheläge"

